Yes, they do.

84
00:04:01,374 --> 00:04:03,176
Has it become a sort of tradition?

85
00:04:03,243 --> 00:04:05,278
I suppose it has.

86
00:04:05,746 --> 00:04:06,713
Somehow it just did.

87
